    <p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0399a02"/><lb ed="T" n="0399a02"/><persName key="A002308">釋法成</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000045053">涼州</placeName>人。十六出家，學通經律。不餌<lb ed="T" n="0399a03"/>五穀，唯食<ptr target="fn02"/>松脂，<ptr target="fn03"/>隱居巖穴，習禪為務。<date key="j18761761886925" notAfter-iso="0454" notBefore-iso="0424">元<lb ed="T" n="0399a04"/>嘉中</date>，<placeName key="PL000000021958">東海</placeName><persName key="A003332">王懷素</persName>出守<placeName key="PL000000036540">巴西</placeName>，聞風遣<ptr target="fn04"/>迎，會<lb ed="T" n="0399a05"/>於<placeName key="PL000000035474">涪城</placeName>。夏坐講律，事竟辭反。因停<placeName key="PL000000035346">廣漢</placeName>，復<lb ed="T" n="0399a06"/>弘禪法。後小疾便告眾<ptr target="fn05"/>云。<persName key="A002308">成</persName>常誦《寶積經》，<lb ed="T" n="0399a07"/>於是自力誦之，始得半卷，氣劣不堪，乃令<lb ed="T" n="0399a08"/>人讀之，一遍<ptr target="fn06"/>纔竟，合掌而卒。侍疾十餘人，<lb ed="T" n="0399a09"/>咸見空<ptr target="fn07"/>中紺馬背負金<ptr target="fn08"/>棺，升空而逝。</p>
